reviewText: My son has autism and is 12, and he is very aware of Bug Rangers and loves this movie! He can see the partial videos on YouTube and this is a really cute cartoon

I didn't like this one as well as the first two I bought. Don't miss the boat and slingshot slugger.
I thoroughly enjoyed them.

I love Amazon!  I don't think I've ever had a bad experience and this time wasn't any different.  Fast shipping.  The product was "as described", new.  As for the video itself, my boys loved it.  It's christian based, which is what I loved.  I didn't have to worry about my boys seeing or hearing something inappropriate.  It had a great message.  WE LOVED IT!!!!
